cts, where the website, campaign, or platform launch looks complete, but the business behind it is still catching up.", "decorations": []}}], "paragraphData": {"textStyle": {"textAlignment": "AUTO"}}}, {"type": "HEADING", "id": "the-takeaway", "nodes": [{"type": "TEXT", "id": "", "nodes": [], "textData": {"text": "The takeaway", "decorations": []}}], "headingData": {"level": 2, "textStyle": {"textAlignment": "AUTO"}}}, {"type": "PARAGRAPH", "id": "qjyll1341", "nodes": [{"type": "TEXT", "id": "", "nodes": [], "textData": {"text": "If the operational layer is not ready, transformation does not fail loudly. It just starts leaking value.", "decorations": []}}], "paragraphData": {"textStyle": {"textAlignment": "AUTO"}}}, {"type": "PARAGRAPH", "id": "fjpk91343", "nodes": [{"type": "TEXT", "id": "", "nodes": [], "textData": {"text": "That leak shows up in manual work, stock issues, slower fulfilment, poor customer experience, and frustrated teams. By the time it becomes visible in the numbers, the business has usually spent months paying for the gap.", "decorations": []}}], "paragraphData": {"textStyle": {"textAlignment": "AUTO"}}}, {"type": "PARAGRAPH", "id": "qp5af1345", "nodes": [{"type": "TEXT", "id": "", "nodes": [], "textData": {"text": "The strongest digital programmes do not just change what the business sells. They change how the business works.", "decorations": []}}], "paragraphData": {"textStyle": {"textAlignment": "AUTO"}}}], "documentStyle": {}}'::jsonb, 2, false, false, '2026-07-11T08:05:18Z');
